    name="Skyler Seegmiller"
    position="AI/ML Engineer"
    aboutMe={`I'm Skyler, an AI/ML engineer with 5 years of experience in machine learning, RAG systems, and scalable AI applications. I specialize in Python, TensorFlow, PyTorch, and integrating advanced AI with frameworks like React and Flask. I also design cloud-native databases with AstraDB, creating user-centric, high-performance solutions optimized for speed, scalability, and reliability. Letâ€™s collaborate to turn ideas into impactful innovations!`}
